            "heading": {
                "type": "heading",
                "content": "Lesson 11: preparing for exams",
                "level": 1
            },
            "items": [
                {
                    "type": "paragraph",
                    "content": "<p>Introduction</p>\n<p>Within a relative short period of time you will have to do 4 exams in English. Your capability and knowledge of your militaru English will be tested.</p>\n<p>There are four tests:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Speaking:  \n<ul>\n<li> Reporting to your commanding officer</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Conversation:\n<ul>\n<li> Having a conversation with a visitor at a checkpoint.</li>\n<li> Informing an English speaking colleague in order to change shifts.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Writing:\n<ul>\n<li>Filling in a report</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Next lessons you will work on assignments and vocabulary which will prepare you to be able to pass. This lesson you will be informed about AAW.<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://maken.wikiwijs.nl/userfiles/c/c9f6f017d2cb6928a8ce7c62fb69bf134367ea21.jpg\" class=\"height-168-pixels width-300-pixels float-right\"/></p>\n"
                }
            ],
            "sections": [
                {
                    "reference": {
                        "value": "3751809"
                    },
                    "heading": {
                        "type": "heading",
                        "content": "Do you behave AAW?",
                        "level": 2
                    },
                    "items": [
                        {
                            "type": "paragraph",
                            "content": "<p>In Great Britain the BBC has participated in a campaign to make people in and outside the army aware of the dangers of working and dealing with AMMO and fireworks.</p>\n<p>This clip is one of the results: Don't gamble with AMMO.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>Watch the clip andmake the assignment.</p>\n<p> </p>\n"
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "video",
                            "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZXxiEZ8rZ_0",
                            "align": "center",
                            "caption": "Don't gamble with AMMO",
                            "poster": "https://img.youtube.com/vi/ZXxiEZ8rZ_0/maxresdefault.jpg"
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "file",
                            "title": "Ammo Gamble",
                            "file": "https://maken.wikiwijs.nl/userfiles/2/2e08baf4bacc98730316a53e639561c70086cfb3.docx"
                        }
                    ],
                    "sections": []
                },
                {
                    "reference": {
                        "value": "3751815"
                    },
                    "heading": {
                        "type": "heading",
                        "content": "How to deal with finding and reporting IED's?",
                        "level": 2
                    },
                    "items": [
                        {
                            "type": "paragraph",
                            "content": "<p>During the MV lessons you have learnt how to handle and report when encountering IED's. It will be a part of your exam. You have been taught how to handle the situation and how to make a report. This is also one of the parts of your final exam.</p>\n<p>To help you you will find a link to a Prezi presentation about AAW. Watch it and then write down all the steps you have to take to report to your commanding officer.</p>\n<p>Go to Its learning and download this assignment.<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://maken.wikiwijs.nl/userfiles/f/fb7408211cd91a6f91b760ca2c884cb6b3a8c334.jpg\" class=\"height-187-pixels width-292-pixels float-right\"/></p>\n"
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "link",
                            "link": "https://prezi.com/udhaxazzufd4/aaw/",
                            "title": "Basic AAW",
                            "description": "A summary of the most important aspects of the AAW procedure",
                            "comment": ""
                        }
                    ],
                    "sections": []
